{
  "stem": "6052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trip in total, if you include Yugoslavia, it was about seven months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seven or eight months altogether.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if we don't include it-- so from Yugoslavia, it was a matter of weeks, of a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, when we left Belgrade, through Saloniki, through Ankara, near the Bosphorus, to Aleppo, and from Aleppo to Beirut, and from Beirut to Rosh HaNikra in Palestine, so it's a matter of a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But altogether was seven or eight months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was through the winter, into the spring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- I can remember a number of people who are-- they're very kind as from the time we left.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at this point, I would like to track back to something quite important which had to do with my living at the Hachshara.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was at the Hachshara while events occurred in Leipzig, where my brother and my sisters were, where they had to deliver their possessions, or our possessions, to the Polizei.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened to me in Steckelsdorf was also not an-- an-- an easy fate because we really produced for the Nazis agricultural items which they needed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, of course, had to work extremely hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was hard labor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this came on top of the hard labor which I had to do in Leipzig on the Pflichtarbeit, which I did not also dwell too much because each Jew had to work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was lucky also with that, because if I were somewhat older, they-- I would have been sent to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they had their rules, their own rules, and they said up to this certain date, nobody is taken-- nobody leaves, but they have to do certain kind of Pflichtarbeit, or whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
